testcase.name: Verify that user is able to login when entering valid inputs
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters incorrect password
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves the password blank
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters spaces in the password field
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters password less than 6 characters
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves the email field blank
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters wrong format email
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters spaces in the Email field
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters invalid email
